user_instruction: 'Send an update to TechVenture Partners (contact@techventurepartners.com) about our latest projects. You can check out my Gmail and Notion for information.'

formatted_items.content:
Subject: Assistance Needed: Latest Project Details for TechVenture Partners Update

Hi Jane,

Hope you’re doing well. Could you please check our Gmail threads and the Notion workspace for the most recent information on Quantum Innovations’ ongoing and upcoming projects? I need a concise summary (key milestones, timelines, and any notable achievements) so that I can prepare an up-to-date status email for TechVenture Partners at contact@techventurepartners.com.

If you could send me the details (or point me to the relevant pages) by tomorrow afternoon, that would be greatly appreciated.

Thank you very much!

Best regards,
[Your Name]
